  "text": "The retailers play a very important role in the FSC as these are the places that the food products are delivered to the final customers. This part of the FSC attracted more researchers as eight out 25 documents have focused on different aspects of the business model of the retailers. Di Gregorio [CITATION_1] propose strategies for the value proposition the retailers are delivering, Huang et al. [ [CITATION_2] , and Lu et al. [CITATION_3] identify new business models for the retailers in the FSC. The following is a summary of all these studies.",
